18
19 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Changes to grants on pro rata basis. Except for the appropriation
20 provided for in [section 1(3)], if money in the cultural and aesthetic projects trust fund account is insufficient to
21 fund projects at the appropriation levels contained in [section 2], reductions to those projects with funding
22 greater than $2,000 must be made on a pro rata basis.
23
24 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Effective date. [This act] is effective July 1, 2025.
